quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  27,23,"Min dey, mi tawii sonnaajo no laamii …ďe homo okkaa immorde e kala hu'unde, no woodami mo kadi jullere [laamu] mawnde."
  27,24,"Mi tawii mo kaŇčko e yim…ďe makko …ďen he…ďe cujjana na'ange nge ga Alla; Seytaane no cu…óani…ďe golle ma…ď…ďe …óen o faddii …ďe ga Laawol ngol, kam…ďe …ďe peewataa."
  27,25,"Ko ha…óata …ďe cujjana Alla oon jaltinoowo ko suu…óii kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi homo Anndi ko cuu…óoton e ko pe√Īinton."
  27,26,"Alla, Dewetee…óo alaa si wonaa KaŇčko Jooma Arsi Tedduki kin."
  27,27,"O maaki: "Aray min ndaara si a gooŇč…óu, maa…óum si laati jiyaa…óo e fen…ďe …ďen"."
  27,28,"Yahdu e nduu talkuru am mberno…óaa ndu ka ma…ď…ďe, refti kuccaa …ďe ndaaraa ko hol…óum …ďe nduttata."
  27,29,"[Sonnaajo on] wi'i: "eey mon mbatu, min dey wernaama ka am talkuru teddundu"."
  27,30,"Pellet, nduu ko immorde e Sulaymaana, pellet, ko woni e mayru ko: "Innde Alla kuu…ďu…óo Yurmeende keerii…óo Yurmeende Oon"."
  27,31,"Wota on townitano kam, ngaree e am ko jebbilii…ďe."
  27,32,"O wi'i: "eey mon mbatu, mba…ótee kam e feere e …óee fiyaake am, mi laataaki ta∆īoowo fiyaake haa tawte…óon e am"."
  27,33,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Enen ko en jooma doole e jooma hare ca…ótu…óe, fiyaake …óen ko ka maa…óa woni, ndaaru ko hol…óum njamirtaa"."
  27,34,"[Debbo on] wi'i: "Pellet, laam…ďe …ďen si …ďe naatii e saare …ďe mbonnat nde, …ďe mba…óa teddu…ďe mayre …ďen hoy…ďe, ko wanonii …ďe ngollirta."
  27,35,"Awa miin, mi nulay e ma…ď…ďe neldaari, mi ndaara ko hol…óum nulaa…ďe …ďen nduttodata."